  "title": "chore(website): remove documentation from website",
  "body": "This removes the documentation process from the website.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- Add Netlify redirections to Algolia documentation\r\n- Move examples to static folder `website/examples` (removed Sass steps)\r\n- Remove `docgen` folder\r\n- Remove development dependencies\r\n\r\n### Links\r\n\r\n- Main website goes to Algolia documentation: https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com\r\n- Stories: https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories\r\n- Examples list goes to Algolia documentation: https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/\r\n- Examples:\r\n  - https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/\r\n  - https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/tourism/\r\n  - https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/media/\r\n  - https://deploy-preview-3396--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/calendar-widget/\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nThe documentation can be safely removed from the source code in other PRs.",
